{"tid":1352710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"728一齊入元朗唔洗怕 唔會主動出手 著齊防具","createTime":"2019-07-22T23:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T00:09:05.000Z","uid":98232,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6133d1b5db941528184df0aa9968f809cd26373e","tid":1352710,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T23:14:07.000Z","msg":"要話比黑社會知香港人唔會怕左佢地<br />\n主線以鄉黑勾結 保衛元朗居民為主<br />\n元朗唔會再有人為自己既政治主張而害怕<br />\n當日著好防具 唔好怕熱 <br />\n學生有唔用既厚書 將佢捲起用膠紙護手臂<br />\n當有刀有棍打埋黎用厚書擋<br />\n用厚書用盾 如果佢地斬埋黎 記者影到<br />\n文宣贏硬 學生以書本抵擋黑社會<br />\n大家齊心協力 記者議員比人打比人斬 <br />\n唔好驚 大家齊心一路大益衝埋去保護佢<br />\n728見"},{"pid":"ac8e245d0fcd7ac38effaac8c5ef978dc2ea26b6","tid":1352710,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T23:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac82a62c38ac4ff3dde2f7623216f1071fbe7f73","tid":1352710,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T23:57:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc31f52d18fa312b14d489c93d5cb91516ce625","tid":1352710,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T23:58:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a30dec9ad4aa9d25222328fe9e0cd9856055d5a1","tid":1352710,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5677199ead448c26aca3edd8c57462581bf63bb9","tid":1352710,"uid":103374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:07:23.000Z","msg":"727吓話？"},{"pid":"0922478312a18129d0ac45a07439e4247269c13e","tid":1352710,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:09:05.000Z","msg":"sor 由佢沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}